{"tid":99231,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，點解仲要生仔","createTime":"2017-01-29T04:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T08:40:24.000Z","uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20f14d12947f2b62fca86d3b40751f600722fba0","tid":99231,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"與其話窮人咪生仔，倒不如諗下，貧富都好，點解要生仔<br />\n有錢人識吃喝玩樂，舒服過窮人，但享樂過後都要捱、煩惱<br />\n一時享樂，官能上滿足、刺激，抵銷不了一個苦字<br />\n我哋大人都頂唔順，點解仲要骨肉承受<br />\n多一份同情，少一條無辜生命"},{"pid":"1c7bd5f45525abf7cebc19ee6c8ade4dec3d0596","tid":99231,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"220a30ae9c3df87164e374b1ceea590c936011ff","tid":99231,"uid":65425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"睇住個B 大好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23815f6cab7934ab960c751a3cc50a7bcd6b81f6","tid":99231,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"養兒防老&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;"},{"pid":"84ff3485da85697cfc6d778046967cec7e805a77","tid":99231,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"點解要製造死亡？"},{"pid":"810e3a8c347c63f0a48340176408a8435ef7219d","tid":99231,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"我認同"}]}